description:
Photo Engraved Pendant in Sterling Silver - Small Heart  (22x20mm)

Select 1 personal picture *, old or new, to have engraved on our high quality Sterling Silver pendant

Our photo pendants are professionally diamond cut and come with UK Hallmark, complete with a stylish pendant bail designed to fit large chains.
